cs.CR, cs.SE, cs.AI, cs.DS, cs.DB

Reasoning: 
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on Android malware analysis and clustering, which falls under the domain of cybersecurity. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is also likely as the paper discusses the design and implementation of an Android malware clustering system. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper utilizes a hierarchical clustering technique, which is a machine learning approach. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is another possible category as the paper uses an efficient bit-vector format to represent Android apps. 
- cs.DB (Databases) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper involves data mining and clustering techniques, which are related to database management.
